&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re so happy you&#39;re here! Thank you for checking our job out and we hope to have the chance to meet you in our interview process!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grüns is one of the fastest-growing brands in the Club channel, and the business is scaling fast. We have active items in the market, new launches in flight, and a third Club retailer on the horizon. We need someone who can own the full channel, not just manage it. This isn&#39;t a maintenance role. It&#39;s a high-stakes, high-visibility seat for someone who wants to run a major retail channel like they built it themselves.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role is part of our remote HQ! &lt;/strong&gt;We have a fully remote, high-trust work environment - and also come together on a biannual basis for amazing off-sites where we can connect IRL. This role also requires quarterly travel to Costco headquarters in Issaquah, Washington.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the full Costco business across the ü Snacks portfolio (including Grüns Adult, Kid’s, and more!). Forecasting, program execution, sell-through management, buyer relationships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive trial and awareness through development and execution of a multi-faceted promotional strategy inclusive of demos, MVM’s, displays in warehouse and .COM, and more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define the Go-To-Market strategy for launch with BJ’s. Establish buyer relationships at HQ, lock assortment and placement, and execute a first-rate in-market launch targeting Q1 2027.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage high performing broker teams - using their support as a multiplier, not a handoff.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Become an indispensable strategic partner through insight-led leadership and flawless fundamentals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of CPG sales experience with at least 2 years calling directly on Costco buyer teams. Existing buyer relationships are a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;ve navigated Costco&#39;s full program toolkit: science binders, TPDs, fence events, MVMs, Costco Connection, CDS demo partnerships, and .com merchandising.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You understand Club channel economics cold. Pack size strategy, display pallet configs, sell-through mechanics, and risk mitigation are your native language.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;ve managed a broker team and know how to get the most out of that partnership without letting them carry the relationship.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a track record of launching new items, executing off-shelf programs, and driving sell-through on LTOs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can build a model, a dashboard, and a buyer presentation from scratch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re fluent in the numbers: GM%, CM2, cost-per-unit, margin math, and syndicated data (SPINS, Nielsen, Numerator).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BJ&#39;s experience is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Approach to the role:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You approach this like a business owner, not an account manager. Strategy, execution, and relationships are all yours.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re obsessive about what happens inside the warehouse and on the .com page. Demo conversion, content quality, and in-stock rates matter as much as the initial sell-in.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You plan quarters ahead. Costco&#39;s fiscal year starts in Sep

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re so happy you&#39;re here! Thank you for checking our job out and we hope to have the chance to meet you in our interview process!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;About the role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grüns is growing fast and we need people who think clearly, move quickly, and help us stay ahead of the curve as we scale. This is a role for someone who wants to be in the room where it happens — not just supporting the work, but driving it. As a BizOps Associate, you&#39;ll be the analytical engine behind some of our biggest growth bets — embedded inside the business, not above it. You&#39;ll own problems end-to-end, from framing the question to driving the answer into action. This role reports directly to our Director of BizOps and sits at the center of how Grüns makes decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role is part of our remote HQ! &lt;/strong&gt;We have a fully remote, high-trust work environment - and also come together on a biannual basis for amazing off-sites where we can connect IRL.&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Identify high-impact business challenges and opportunities, structure them as problems worth solving, and drive analysis that leads to a clear recommendation — not just a report&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Build and own financial models that forecast the impact of new strategies, pricing decisions, and growth initiatives, and hold yourself accountable to measuring actual performance against those forecasts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Partner directly with senior leaders across retail, DTC, marketing, and operations to answer their hardest questions — and proactively surface the questions they haven&#39;t thought to ask yet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Design and run tests: develop hypotheses, build the analytical framework, execute, and translate results into decisions the business can act on&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Own ad hoc analysis and KPI reporting for key stakeholders — building infrastructure that becomes a lasting resource, not a one-time deliverable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Support new product and pricing strategy with modeling and market analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Evaluate new growth channels and optimize existing ones across our DTC and retail business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who has:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS/MS Degree in a quantitative or computational field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years experience in data analytics in corporate, consulting, or investment banking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication skills with technical and non-technical audiences, able to influence your partners using clear, concise insights and recommendations through strong data-driven analyses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High proficiency with Excel/Google Sheets and PowerPoint/Google Slides&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise with SQL, with R and/or Python knowledge preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional thought partnership skills, able to own direct relationships with stakeholders and build credibility through clarity and judgment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong statistical skills and intuition for solving problems in both consumer-facing and internal product areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Cloud Computing (Google Cloud) platforms preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Approach to the role:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re so happy you&#39;re here! Thank you for checking our job out and we hope to have the chance to meet you in our interview process!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The CFO’s mission is to continue building upon Grüns&#39; already strong finance and data function — evolving it into a best-in-class engine that empowers the entire organization to make faster, smarter decisions. Leading a team of three strong leaders, this role is about leading the strong teams below them to democratize financial intelligence across the Grüns organization: self-serve dashboards, on-demand reporting, and real-time visibility that puts decision-making power in the hands of every team member.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The CFO is a relentless, collaborative business partner, never satisfied with where the business is on revenue scale or profitability, always pushing for the next point of EBITDA margin improvement across all functions and driving efficiency to fuel continued revenue growth. They will ensure Grüns scales with confidence while meeting all external requirements seamlessly in the background.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role is part of our remote HQ! &lt;/strong&gt;We have a fully remote, high-trust work environment - and also come together on a biannual basis for amazing off-sites where we can connect IRL.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;What success looks like:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;If we look ahead a year from now, the right person in this role would have:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leveraged what we’ve built so far, found areas for improvement, and fully operationalized a goal accountability framework that keeps business initiatives tied to financial outcomes, ensuring the leadership team is consistently tracking toward revenue and profitability targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Driven meaningful EBITDA margin improvement across all functions and improved LTV:CAC efficiency to fuel continued revenue growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Delivered self-serve dashboards, templatized reporting, and real-time P&amp;amp;L visibility across functions so every team has the data access they need without relying on ad-hoc requests. Business decisions are democratized and exponentially quicker.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Created the conditions for a high-performing, motivated team empowering vs. micromanaging, actively developing leaders, and driving strong results and performance without burnout.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Built the systems and processes to meet all external reporting and compliance requirements seamlessly, keeping the team focused on growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone with:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Relentless Growth Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Always asking what it takes to get to the next level, whether that&#39;s another point of margin, better efficiency, or a faster path to revenue growth - a genuine internal drive to make the business the best it can be. Finding new opportunities across the business and proposing these opportunities to the CEO and functional leads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Integrity and Business-First Thinking:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Prioritizes the truth over “looking good”. Navigates competing stakeholder interests honestly and thoroughly rather than taking the path of least resistance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Empowering Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Leads by giving people the tools, clarity, and confidence to make great&lt;br&gt;dec

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re so happy you&#39;re here! Thank you for checking our job out and we hope to have the chance to meet you in our interview process!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ü Snacks is scaling fast, with a growing portfolio of brands and a launch pipeline that never slows down. We need a &lt;strong&gt;Director of GTM &amp;amp; Business Strategy&lt;/strong&gt; to own the full product and campaign launch lifecycle end-to-end: from concept through post-launch analysis, across every brand in our portfolio. This is the connective tissue role — the person who keeps launches on time, teams aligned, and leadership informed, without needing anyone above them to chase it down. You&#39;ll report directly to VP, GTM and be the operational backbone turning ambitious launch calendars into flawless market entries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role is part of our remote HQ! &lt;/strong&gt;We have a fully remote, high-trust work environment - and also come together on a biannual basis for amazing off-sites where we can connect IRL.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Project Management &amp;amp; Operational Planning&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the full product launch lifecycle from concept through post-launch analysis, building comprehensive timelines that establish critical path milestones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive accountability across teams by maintaining stakeholder alignment to deadlines and centralized documentation for all launch plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure operational readiness by coordinating inventory, packaging, and fulfillment requirements while managing timelines to prevent bottlenecks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Stakeholder Alignment &amp;amp; Communication&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead strategic kickoff meetings and deliver structured updates to executive leadership, providing visibility into progress and risk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the essential connective tissue between departments, translating complex project details into clear, actionable information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use a deep understanding of company strategy to spot roadblocks early and drive swift resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Process Improvement &amp;amp; Scalability&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Iterate on standardized GTM playbooks and post-launch retros, continuously sharpening how we plan and execute launches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design scalable processes and optimize project management tools to support a growing, multi-brand launch calendar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build improved AI-powered processes and reporting for full launch program management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help clarify the ROI of past launches and shape launch strategy heading into future years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has 8-10+ years in project management or GTM/strategic operations within DTC, CPG, or eCommerce, with the organizational muscle to run multiple complex projects at once&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excels at cross-functional leadership across product, finance, operations, and marketing, with real proficiency in project management platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Brings strong strategic thinking and business acumen — has built standardized launch templates and led thoughtful capacity planning before&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Makes data-driven decisions using post-launch metrics while keeping sight of the bigger business picture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
