&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re so happy you&#39;re here! Thank you for checking our job out and we hope to have the chance to meet you in our interview process!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grüns is building one of the most exciting live e-commerce studios in the country, and we&#39;re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Livestream Host&lt;/strong&gt; to be the face of it. This is a performance role — you&#39;ll be on camera, selling Grüns products live to a real audience, and bringing the energy that turns viewers into customers. If you&#39;re magnetic, coachable, and genuinely love being in front of people, this role was made for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; On-site, Culver City, CA (in-studio)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt; This role starts part-time at ~20 hours/week, with the potential to grow to full-time as the studio scales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employment type:&lt;/strong&gt; Hourly W2&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay:&lt;/strong&gt; Starting at $45/hr + commission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Host live selling streams on TikTok and other platforms, driving product engagement and sales in real time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver compelling, on-brand product presentations — knowing the product inside and out and making it feel natural on camera&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interact with the live audience through chat, questions, and real-time engagement to keep the energy high and viewers watching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow direction from the production team and adapt quickly between streams and formats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Film short-form content to supplement live streams and contribute to brainstorming and ideation for social content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the Grüns brand with consistency, enthusiasm, and authenticity every time you go live&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has experience in front of a camera — live streaming, acting, improv, or a performance-adjacent background (e.g., fitness instruction, teaching, hosting)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is genuinely comfortable being on camera for extended periods and can hold an audience&#39;s attention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has a basic understanding of consumer products and customer-facing communication — retail, service, or sales experience is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has sold or presented on TikTok Live, Instagram Live, or a similar platform (preferred, not required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has Twitch experience or a familiarity with live audience culture (bonus)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Approach to the role:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take direction well and implement feedback fast — you&#39;re coachable and don&#39;t take notes personally&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You do the homework. You know the product, understand who you&#39;re selling to, and show up prepared&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You bring the energy even on shift four of the week — consistency on camera is your baseline, not your ceiling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re flexible and can pivot when the format, product, or direction changes mid-stream&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take ownership of your performance and are always looking for ways to improve your craft&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;3817&quot; data-end=&quot;4179&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3817&quot; data-end=&quot;3830&quot;&gt;To Apply:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3817&quot

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re so happy you&#39;re here! Thank you for checking our job out and we hope to have the chance to meet you in our interview process!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grüns is building a live commerce studio from the ground up, and the &lt;strong&gt;Livestream Operator&lt;/strong&gt; is the person who makes every stream run without a hitch. This is a technical and production role — you&#39;ll own the back end of every broadcast, keep talent supported and on track, and ensure the viewer experience is seamless from start to finish. If you&#39;re a self-starter who thrives in a fast-paced production environment and knows how to keep things moving without being told twice, this is your role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; On-site, Culver City, CA (in-studio)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt; This role starts part-time at ~20 hours/week, with the potential to grow to full-time as the studio scales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Employment type:&lt;/strong&gt; Hourly W2&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay:&lt;/strong&gt; $35/hr + commission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the technical side of each live stream — equipment setup, stream configuration, and real-time troubleshooting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run back-end platform functions during broadcasts, including flash sales, giveaways, and other live commerce features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moderate the live chat — keeping it on-brand, engaging, and free of distractions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support talent throughout every stream — coordinating logistics so hosts can stay focused on performing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make occasional on-camera appearances as needed in a supporting capacity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Film short-form content to supplement live streams and contribute to brainstorming and ideation for social content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has experience in production — whether on a film or TV set, in a studio environment, or in a technical live event capacity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is comfortable operating production equipment and platforms without hand-holding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has worked closely with on-camera talent and knows how to create an environment where they can do their best work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has experience with live streaming platforms (TikTok Live, YouTube Live, OBS, or similar) — or picks up new tools fast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Is highly reliable — this is a shift-based role and showing up prepared, on time, and ready to execute is non-negotiable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Approach to the role:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You anticipate problems before they happen and fix them before anyone else notices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re calm under pressure — when something goes sideways mid-stream, you handle it without making it a moment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take ownership of your environment. The studio, the stream, the chat — it&#39;s all yours to manage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re a team player who genuinely cares about making the hosts successful, even if you&#39;re mostly working behind the scenes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re consistent and accountable. Every shift, same standard.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
