&lt;p data-start=&quot;3

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re so happy you&#39;re here! Thank you for checking our job out and we hope to have the chance to meet you in our interview process!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We need a &lt;strong&gt;Creative Producer&lt;/strong&gt; who lives and breathes paid social. UGC video editing. Native-format static ads. Remix cuts that turn one winning concept into ten variations. Lo-fi content that stops the scroll because it feels real, not because it looks expensive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be making the ads that millions of people see in their feeds every day, across five brands and very different audiences. You&#39;ll know what&#39;s working because you&#39;ll watch the performance data — and you&#39;ll keep producing, because that&#39;s what you love: create at pace, learn from results, get better every cycle.&lt;/p&gt;
