&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Shipping and Receiving Associate&lt;/strong&gt;, you will support the fulfillment process by executing daily tasks in picking, packing, and shipping while maintaining inventory accuracy through effective receiving and cycle counts. You&#39;ll work collaboratively within a high-performing team, meeting established KPIs, and participating in continuous improvement initiatives. With attention to quality standards and operational excellence, you&#39;ll contribute to on-time deliveries and accurate inventory systems while following established processes and procedures. This role will report directly to the Shipping and Receiving Supervisor.&lt;/p&gt;
