&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate system data, including inventory levels, bin locations, and lot tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help maintain a clean, organized, and safe work environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with additional warehouse operations as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
